articles.author: Ariel Edwards-Levy, CNN
articles.title: Fewer than one-third of Americans want to see Roe v. Wade overturned, new polling finds - CNN
articles.description: Fewer than one-third of Americans want to see the Roe v. Wade decision overturned, according to a set of three polls released over the past week, with key elements of Texas' restrictive new abortion law also garnering relatively little support in the polls.
